(621, 38, 'description_2', '<div class=\"bannerp banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row center site-co\">\r\n<div class=\"prods\">\r\n\r\nHONESTY, INTEGRITY, LEADERSHIP, AND PROSPERITY. - Our mission is to provide our customers with the highest quality, and best service in the industry while keeping our products affordable for everybody by improving our market and products, following the developing technology. - Fully support our business partners in fair and exhibitions conducted in Egypt and abroad.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"site-con\"></div>'),
