(1242, 105, '_title_3', 'field_593f1bbdc7309'),
(1243, 105, 'description_3', '- Providing wide range of quality products using the latest technology, at affordable prices while serving and meeting customers’ needs and expectations, by transforming our Egyptian quality stones into designs that provide beauty and wellness.\r\n\r\n- To represent the Egyptian quality stones all over the world by importing and making good relations with suppliers in the provision of these raw materials and transfer to other countries at competitive prices.\r\n\r\n- The transfer of imported raw materials to be manufactured in our factory in Egypt to re-export, taking advantage of the features found in Egypt from a lack of manufacturing prices of labor, electricity, water and taxes.\r\n\r\n- The use of equipment and skilled labor to work on the shapes, poles, carvings, architectural decoration using Egyptian marble and imported stone and that’s for major and minor projects.'),
