(35, 1, '2017-06-12 22:55:33', '2017-06-12 22:55:33', 'In 1984 we started with a small company, called “el Ezz” company, its activity was only supplying and installing of marble. In 1991, Sinai factory for marble and granite was established. Few years later, we became one of the best in the export field. In 1992, Onix Company was established to later become a leading integrated of import. As of 2007, Onix and Sinai merged under the name of Onix handling both, the import and export of Marble and Granite in Egypt.\r\n\r\nOur main strength is to promote quality Egyptian Marble and Granite to the worldwide business sector and adding the touch of the latest technology to these materials to achieve today\'s legend. Couple of years after, we turn out to be broadly and globally conspicuous producer and exporter in Marble and Granite division. We are committed to meeting and exceeding our customer’s expectations by providing extraordinary workmanship and excellent service. We meet our commitments in a reliable and professional manner so our customers can be satisfied.', 'ABOUT US', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-06-30 03:16:30', '2017-06-30 03:16:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/onix/?page_id=35', 0, 'page', '', 0),
